nd music composed by the famous group project lights<br>+◇ Unique costumes and weapons!<br>+◇ Fully customized your own experience. <br>+◇ Customizable cut scenes: Try out our new portrait mode! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662960/extras/6de2fc79f82e68716118b3cfccd09c4d.poster.avif?t=1771507041\" width=400 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662960/extras/6de2fc79f82e68716118b3cfccd09c4d.webm?t=1771507041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662960/extras/6de2fc79f82e68716118b3cfccd09c4d.mp4?t=1771507041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662960/extras/bddebbb93f67e3b806baf5cba628fb41.poster.avif?t=1771507041\" width=356 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662960/extras/bddebbb93f67e3b806baf5cba628fb41.webm?t=1771507041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662960/extras/bddebbb93f67e3b806baf5cba628fb41.mp4?t=1771507041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662960/extras/d4eb23b8c3ed67a1123abf20f6c39d78.poster.avif?t=1771507041\" width=356 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662960/extras/d4eb23b8c3ed67a1123abf20f6c39d78.webm?t=1771507041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662960/extras/d4eb23b8c3ed67a1123abf20f6c